%F A037580 From _Colin Barker_, Dec 27 2012: (Start)
%F A037580 a(n) = (11*8^n + 7*(-1)^n - 18)/63.
%F A037580 a(n) = 8*a(n-1) + a(n-2) - 8*a(n-3).
%F A037580 G.f.: x*(3*x+1)/((x-1)*(x+1)*(8*x-1)). (End)
